{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"d8f499a8-10a6-5f2e-b5f3-fc740040108a","excerpt":"Given two sorted integer arrays nums1 and nums2, merge nums2 into nums1 as one sorted array. Note: The number of elements initialized in…","html":"<p>Given two sorted integer arrays nums1 and nums2, merge nums2 into nums1 as one sorted array.</p>\n<p>Note:</p>\n<p>The number of elements initialized in nums1 and nums2 are m and n respectively.\nYou may assume that nums1 has enough space (size that is greater or equal to m + n) to hold additional elements from nums2.</p>\n<h3 id=\"题目类型分析\"><a href=\"#%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>题目类型分析</h3>\n<p>Merge Sort 算法题目，尽可能往这个方向上考虑具体思路。<br>\n如果不能第一时间想到 Merge Sort 说明数据结构和算法基础需要复习，补好基础继续解题才是正确的路。</p>\n<h3 id=\"解法\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%B3%95\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解法</h3>\n<p>现有条件相当于 merge sort 剩最后 2 个子数组，直接比较各自元素再 merge 。<br>\n<strong>题目有限制，要求直接修改 nums1，如果使用额外空间会报错</strong>，需要对合并步骤做一些调整。\n题目说明 nums1 长度足够，从数组尾部开始，从后往前向 nums1 中复制元素就可以了，步骤如下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>比较 nums1 和 nums2 初始尾部元素大小，大的那个移动到 nums1 未使用的尾部</li>\n<li>重复以上步骤，依次把二个子数组当前最大元素复制到 nums1 的尾部，直至二者其中之一所有元素都已复制</li>\n<li>因为是将 nums2 元素合并到 nums1 中，所以只需要考虑剩余数组是 nums2 的情况，继续赋值 nums2 的元素，直至将 nums1 数组填满</li>\n<li>新的 nums1 就是合并后的结果，结束</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"类似题目\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E4%BC%BC%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%AE\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类似题目</h3>\n<p>不同数据结构的类似题目</p>\n<ol>\n<li>[LeetCode 21] Merge Two Sorted List</li>\n<li>[LeetCode 617] Merge Two Binary Trees</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 12, 2019","title":"[LeetCode 88] Merge Sorted Array","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5056179775280898,"src":"/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/d7b72/post-default-bg.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/2347c/post-default-bg.jpg 750w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/5a448/post-default-bg.jpg 1500w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/d7b72/post-default-bg.jpg 3000w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/439d2/post-default-bg.jpg 4288w","sizes":"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Blog/[LeetCode 88] Merge Sorted Array/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Blog/[LeetCode 461] Hamming Distance/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[LeetCode 461] Hamming Distance"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Blog/[LeetCode 278] First Bad Version/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[LeetCode 278] First Bad Version"}}}}